# CLIP ChangeLog for app-clip/clip-beacon

*clip-beacon-0.1.2-r3 (14 Dec 2017)

  14 Dec 2017; Nicolas Belouin <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-beacon-0.1.2-r3.ebuild, -clip-beacon-0.1.2-r2.ebuild:
  Fix little mistype on optional packages probe.

*clip-beacon-0.1.2-r2 (28 Nov 2017)

  28 Nov 2017; Nicolas Belouin <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-beacon-0.1.2-r2.ebuild, -clip-beacon-0.1.2-r1.ebuild:
  Add more data to the beacon, now with gateways, videomode, optional packages,
  timezone, hardware status.


  28 Nov 2017; Tony Cheneau <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  files/scripts/02-basic_info, files/_debian/postinst: 
  Make beacon "beam" data less frequently (once per hour as opposed to each five minutes
  List all users of the system (as opposed to only privusers.

