*clip-beacon-0.1.2 (25 Feb 2015)

  25 Feb 2015; Hugo Chargois <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-beacon-0.1.2.ebuild, -clip-beacon-0.1.1.ebuild:
  clip-beacon-send: improvements in how the HTTP POST body is made.

*clip-beacon-0.1.1 (24 Feb 2015)

  24 Feb 2015; Hugo Chargois <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-beacon-0.1.1.ebuild, -clip-beacon-0.1.0.ebuild:
  clip-beacon-send: do not print the HTTP response contents to stdout, but
  exit with an error if the HTTP status is not 2xx.

